subject: College Athletics
Lacrosse
NCAA Lacrosse Championships
lead_paragraph: A face-off victory late in the game was critical in helping the Blue Devils’ John Danowski become the ninth men’s lacrosse coach to win three N.C.A.A. Division I championships.
